om/artists/future">Future</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">Kanye West</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-cudi">Kid Cudi</a>出演）以来的首张完整专辑。</p><p>发行后，Carti 继续与 ABRA 合作制作了 2021 年单曲“Unlock It”，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trippie-redd">与 Trippie Redd</a>合作制作了歌曲“Miss The Rage”，以及最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-teams-up-with-madonna-and-playboi-carti-for-new-track-popular-listen-here-3450944">与麦当娜合作的“Popular”和周末</a>。</p><p>它出现在由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">威肯</a>和莉莉-罗丝·德普主演的 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">HBO</a>剧集<em>《偶像》</em>中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/playboi-carti-appears-to-postpone-antagonist-tour-again-3567716">Playboi Carti 似乎推迟“Antagonist”巡演的消息再次</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
