g Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attention》就获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-smile-a-light-for-attracting-attention-radiohead-thom-yorke-jonny-greenwood-3222308"><em>《NME》</em>的四星好评</a>，评价为“展示了约克与格林伍德合作伙伴关系的旋律优美、更有活力和自由流畅的迭代”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-smile-new-single-friend-of-a-friend-announce-wall-of-eyes-cinema-album-playback-events-3567721">The Smile 的帖子分享了令人惊叹的新单曲“Friend Of A Friend”，并宣布特别的“Wall Of Eyes”电影专辑播放活动</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
