0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/1dVYKimIL2LNZ060VMhX33?si=2e7fc88cb4d54397&#038;nd=1&#038;dlsi=8c665212d9d54400&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>这首歌是乐队继 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shed-seven-share-folksy-new-song-talk-of-the-town-3554797">《Talk Of The Town》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-shed-sevens-reflective-new-single-starlings-3525769">《Starlings》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aKLe8-npCTw">《Kissing California》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m_2PtCZxZJ0">《F:K:H》</a>和由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">Happy Mondays</a>歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rowetta">Rowetta</a>演唱的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shed-seven-share-new-single-featuring-rowetta-and-talk-guest-heavy-album-a-matter-of-time-3505094">In Ecstasy</a> 》之后的第六首歌曲。</p><p>他们的新唱片于上周五（1 月 5 日）发行，目前有望夺得本周英国排名第一的专辑。</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/shed-seven-a-matter-of-time-number-1-albums-chart/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>官方排行榜公司</em></a>的数据，它领先于本周排行榜冠军<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lewis-capaldi">刘易斯·卡帕尔迪 (Lewis Capaldi</a> ) 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lewis-capaldi-broken-by-desire-to-be-heavenly-sent-review-3444656">《Broken By Desire To Be Heavenly Sent》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/busted">Busted</a>的最新版本《Greatest Hits 2.0》。</p><p> Witter 最近告诉<em>NME</em> ：“我认为这对我们来说将是重要的一年，从我们首张专辑《Change Giver》30 周年纪念第一周发行的全新专辑开始。如果您是七号棚的粉丝，我认为您应该系好安全带，因为您将会享受到愉快的旅程。如果你不是粉丝，就找一块大石头，躲在它后面。”</p><p>在其他消息中，七棚乐队将于今年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/blossoms-announce-huge-outdoor-manchester-show-for-summer-2024-buy-tickets-3528789">在曼彻斯特威森肖公园举行的大型户外音乐会上为 Blossoms 表演开场支持</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hear-shed-sevens-pete-doherty-collab-throwaways-as-band-head-for-number-one-with-new-album-356766